{"tid":1696281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"豬膶名店「漢發」缺乏愛國心，老闆明言不歡迎領導人及民族英雄入內進食","createTime":"2019-11-06T05:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T07:23:00.000Z","uid":202464,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"51e8bb334d8a892e0b4369d4e941bdafc19a357f","tid":1696281,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"在過去的周日有網民圖文並茂指，阿叻幫襯豬膶名店漢發時發表曱甴論，還得到老闆娘熱情招待。事發一日，我們找到老闆回應：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問：「你會不會叫陳百祥近期不要來？」<br />\n答：「我都會和他說聲，在這個敏感時期你都是買外賣吧！」<br />\n<br />\n問：「但你會接待警察嗎？」<br />\n答：「如果他們穿着制服入來，我會向他說聲不好意思，警察先生不如你買外賣吧！」<br />\n<br />\n答：「如果特首來，我不是太歡迎，不如你去買外賣，不要在這裏。」"},{"pid":"fda96c56984adf88d6a099c05f60682652b60020","tid":1696281,"uid":94227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:46:56.000Z","msg":"買外賣啦"},{"pid":"bc8dd7fa3ad68774a074e4ee6b5ec75322a60e5c","tid":1696281,"uid":202464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"小資老闆不識抬舉，藐視國家領導人及民族英雄！"},{"pid":"43ecfab3a560b8a800820ba07e6320cf1ac6cbd1","tid":1696281,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:51:12.000Z","msg":"乳滑者雖遠必豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不能忍了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465c9fb2ace1e679c1d74a420540e88bd6ee93e6","tid":1696281,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:53:01.000Z","msg":"愛國青年應該聲討呢間野。<br />\n<br />\n特首肯光顧應該跪地相迎啦。"},{"pid":"a414b00a1a9983df03dd1c669f6834022d9039cc","tid":1696281,"uid":117420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T05:54:06.000Z","msg":"人人得而誅之<br />\n我支持警察 你可以唔比豬潤麵我啦"},{"pid":"545d4444e3981060744859ea96681e2b7fe9ba6f","tid":1696281,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T0